title: [XPX] JARDesign Airbus A320neo v1.4
description:
Hi simmers,

This is my first post and I'll be seeding as long as I can !

Here is the wonderfull A320neo by JARDesign.
It's the 1.4 version found in comments on TPB.
Working with both x32 and x64 versions of X-PLANE 10 on both MAC & PC !

This is not the latest version but since I can't find v2.x on the web...
If someone has the latest update or crack please share it ! 


INSTALLATION :

Simply unzip and copy in your "Aircraft" folder !
